---
const title = "About Finical 3D";
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{title}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/finical3d-main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <Nav />

    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="about-hero-content">
            <h1 class="hero-title">
                <span class="line"><span><span></span>The Tools<br>of</span></span>
                <span class="line"><span class="accent">Finical 3D</span></span>
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-description">
                High quality 3D printers, scanners, and CAD software for precision design and prototyping.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="featured">
        <div class="featured-container">

            <div class="featured-hero">
                <div class="featured-content">
                    <span class="label">Our Tools</span>
                    <h2>High-Quality Equipment</h2>
                    <p> We provide state-of-the-art 3D printers, scanners, and CAD software to ensure precision and quality in every project.
                Our tools are designed to meet the highest standards of performance and reliability, enabling us to deliver exceptional results for our clients.</p>
                    <h2>Our Capabilities</h2>
                    <p>With our advanced equipment, we can handle a wide range of projects, from simple prototypes to complex end-use parts. Our team is skilled in utilizing these tools to their fullest potential, ensuring that each project meets the highest standards of quality and efficiency.</p>
                    <img src="/images/tools.avif" alt="Tools" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>Precision tools for precision results.</p>
                                        <h2>Elegoo Centauri Carbon</h2>
                    <img src="/images/elegoocentauri.avif" alt="Centauri" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>Our FDM printers offer exceptional detail and surface finish for a wide range of applications. This printer is capable of printing in a wide range of filament types. With a fully enclosed build volume, engineering grade filament can be used for robust and durable prints.</p>
                    <p>Our hard working buddy.</p>
                                                            <h2>Elegoo Mars 5 Ultra</h2>
                    <img src="/images/elegoomars5ultra.avif" alt="Mars 5 Ultra" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>Meet the Elegoo Mars 5 Ultra, our latest resin printer designed for high-resolution printing and exceptional detail. With a high resolution of 2560 x 1440 pixels, it delivers stunning results for intricate models.</p>
                    <p>Our artistic companion.</p>
                                                                                <h2>Elegoo Mercury 3.0 Plus</h2>
                    <img src="/images/elegoomercury.avif" alt="Mercury" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>The cleaning station required to do the dirty work and provide your prints with a flawless finish. With advanced uv curing technology, it ensures consistent and high-quality results.</p>
                    <p>Our scrubbing sentinel.</p>
                                                                                                    <h2>Creality Otter</h2>
                    <img src="/images/crealityotter.avif" alt="Otter" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>The Otter is a reliable scanner designed for high-quality 3D scanning and modeling. With up to 0.02mm resolution, it captures fine details with exceptional accuracy.</p>
                    <p>Our precision partner.</p>
                                                                                                                 <h2>Powered by Fusion</h2>
                    <img src="/images/fusion360.avif" alt="Fusion 360" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>Fusion 360® is a powerful cloud-based CAD/CAM software that enables seamless design and manufacturing workflows. With its intuitive interface and robust feature set, it empowers users to create, simulate, and manufacture innovative products with ease.</p>
                    <p>Our design powerhouse.</p>
                                                                                                                               <h2>Handy Tools</h2>
                    <img src="/images/handytools.avif" alt="Handy Tools" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>A collection of essential tools for maintaining and operating our 3D printing equipment. From basic maintenance supplies to specialized accessories, we have everything you need to keep your setup running smoothly.</p>
                    <p>Our trusty companions.</p>
                    <br>

                    <a href="/#contact" class="feature-cta">Get In Touch</a>
                    <br>
                </div>
                <div class="featured-image-section">
                    <div class="featured-image-grid">
                        <div class="featured-img">
                            <img src="/images/3dprint1.avif">
                        </div>
                         to move towards a fully circular economy in our 3D printing operations, where waste is minimized and resources are utilized to their fullest potential.</p>
                    <img src="/images/clean.avif" alt="Cleanup" style="width: 150px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p>One cleaner print for a greener future.</p>
                    <a href="/#contact" class="feature-cta">Get In Touch</a>
                </div>
                <div class="featured-image-section">
                    <div class="featured-image-grid">
                        <div class="featured-img">
                            <img src="/images/3dprint1.avif">
                        </div>
                        <div class="featured-img">
                            <img src="/images/3dprint2.avif">
                        </div>
                        <div class="featured-img">
                            <img src="/images/3dprint3.avif">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-highlights" style="margin-top: 60px;">
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <div class="highlight-icon">🖨️</div>
                    <div class="highlight-title">3D Printing</div>
                    <div class="highlight-desc">Custom FDM and resin printing services for prototypes and end-use parts</div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <div class="highlight-icon">📐</div>
                    <div class="highlight-title">CAD Design</div>
                    <div class="highlight-desc">Reverse engineering and original CAD modelling for any application</div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <div class="highlight-icon">🔍</div>
                    <div class="highlight-title">3D Scanning</div>
                    <div class="highlight-desc">High-accuracy scanning to capture real-world objects as digital models</div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <div class="highlight-icon">🌱</div>
                    <div class="highlight-title">Sustainable</div>
                    <div class="highlight-desc">Closed-loop filament recycling and eco-conscious manufacturing</div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <div class="highlight-icon">🇳🇿</div>
                    <div class="highlight-title">NZ Owned</div>
                    <div class="highlight-desc">Proudly local, serving clients across New Zealand</div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <div class="highlight-icon">👑</div>
                    <div class="highlight-title">Premium Quality</div>
                    <div class="highlight-desc">Only the finest filaments and resins used in every print</div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>
    <span>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; text-align: center; padding: 20px;"><br>"Autodesk, the Autodesk logo, and Fusion 360 are registered trademarks or trademarks of Autodesk, Inc., and/or its subsidiaries and/or affiliates in the USA and other countries."</p><br>
    </span>
    <Footer />

    <script is:inline src="/finical3d-scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

<style>
    .about-hero {
        min-height: 50vh;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #000;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .about-hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        padding: 140px 50px 80px;
        max-width: 800px;
    }

    .feature-highlights {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .feature-highlights {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .about-hero-content {
            padding: 120px 20px 60px;
        }
    }
</style>